description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesday. This is round 3 of 4 of the December match up between The Dragons and the Goddesses. This is the Semi-Final match.
The final wrestling round of this great match gets started and the Blue team is behind. They get a couple great double teams and rack up some points but Orange is just too skilled and powerful. Ami Emerson and Holly heart get there asses kicked. The fight a valiant fight, but they are just overpowered! Stay tuned next week to watch the winners fuck the holy bejesus out of the losers.
title: The Dragons vs The Goddesses
